body:
Compose your Docs with Ease. Compose is a lean Hugo domentation theme, inspired by forestry.io.
Feel free to open a PR, raise an issue(s) or request new feature(s).  You can generate diagrams, flowcharts, and piecharts from text in a similar manner as markdown using mermaid.
Or, generate graphs, charts and tables from a csv, or a json file.
 Read the DocsDownload Theme
title: Compose
